creator: Fernando Pessoa
description:
LibriVox recording of 35 Sonnets by Fernando Pessoa. (Translated by Anonymous.)
Read in English by Anusha Iyer; Ross Klatte; Ryan Finch; Jude; Greg Giordano; Ian King; Kathrine Engan
While Fernando Pessoa is internationally now known mostly for his masterpiece The Book of Disquiet, he was also an outstanding poet. 35 of his sonnets are collected in this volume. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
